== Marian tenewen ==
[[Karrek|Karrygi]] terrys dhyworth tenwennow an nans gans [[Ober rewi-teudhi|ober rewi-teudhi]] a godh avel [[radel]] dhe denewen an rewliv. An rewliv ynwedh a herdh rewtinyow lows dhe'n tenwennow. Hemm a furv marian tenewen.

== Marian kres ==
Pan wrello dew rewliv metya, an marianow tenewen a jun dhe furvya marian kres. Y hwelir marianow kres avel skethow tewl a-hys an rewliv.

